ort of moderator, but he doesn\u2019t have the mod badge.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHe was one of the earlier and busier moderators.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u002227914\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed9334365006\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/158494-sal_vager-is-leaving-to-travel-the-world%C2%A0/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Souptime","CreatedById":204451,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-16T02:45:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223989215\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221623714716\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002227914\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vanamonde\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 6/14/2021 at 7:51 PM, Vanamonde said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat\u0027s this about Supernovy\u0027s tent?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni was reading the first 30-35 pages of the thread (Which was around late 2015), and something about \u0022Supernovy\u0027s tent\u0022 was going around, apparently it might be some sort of disaster, idk\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-16T02:52:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI do not recall. Perhaps \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/29617-supernovy/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002229617\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/29617-supernovy/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Supernovy\u003C/a\u003E does.\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Admiral Fluffy","CreatedById":210816,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-16T02:56:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat was the 2013 forum incident? Also, what was the Great forum migration of 2015?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, who is \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/12858-red-iron-crown/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002212858\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/12858-red-iron-crown/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Red Iron Crown\u003C/a\u003E? Is he a former mod?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-06-16T02:59:28Z\u0022 title=\u002206/16/2021 02:59  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EJune 16, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by Admiral Fluffy\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EMoar questions\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-16T03:02:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat was the 2013 forum incident?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSomething went wrong and when they tried to revert to a saved backup of the forum, the last viable save turned out to be 7 months old. I don\u0027t know why. I wasn\u0027t a moderator at the time. But months\u0027 worth of posts, threads, and new accounts were undone.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#f9f9f9;color:#2d3134;font-size:15px;\u0022\u003EAlso, what was the Great forum migration of 2015?\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe transitioned from one forum software to another.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#f9f9f9;color:#2d3134;font-size:15px;\u0022\u003EAlso, who is\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/12858-red-iron-crown/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002212858\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/12858-red-iron-crown/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022 style=\u0022font-size:13.5px;padding:.1em .8em;\u0022\u003E@Red Iron Crown\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#f9f9f9;color:#2d3134;font-size:15px;\u0022\u003E? Is he a former mod?\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Souptime","CreatedById":204451,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-16T05:13:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat are the steps to becoming a moderator? do you need to be a specific age?\u00A0\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:8px;\u0022\u003Eis there a cool cult initiation in a dark room with black robes?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-16T05:28:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe process of becoming a mod is actually quite grueling (I can say this as I did it just a few years ago). First, you must prepare your body by shaving everywhere and covering yourself in peanut butter. Then there\u0027s the physical, where you are tested for endurance and agility by running a 10km obstacle course in subzero temperatures while carrying a backpack full of wet sand. After that, you must write a 1000-word essay about the spirit of the KSP community and how you will preserve and protect it. That done, you move on to the Reverse Captcha, where you must read 1000 posts and determine which ones are spambots, miss more than one and you\u0027re out. Finally, after you have completed those tasks, you must submit your moderator registration fee of $1000 in cash to UomoCapra and he\u0027ll make you a moderator.\u003Csup\u003E[1]\u003C/sup\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn my case, I was approached by \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/149302-darth-badie/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022149302\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/149302-darth-badie/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Darth Badie\u003C/a\u003E, who asked me if I was interested in being part of the moderator team. I said yes (after asking a bunch of questions), signed an \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Non-Disclosure Agreement\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Non-Disclosure Agreement\u0022\u003ENDA\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E, and was given a whole bunch of moderator permissions and access. We very much throw new moderators in the deep end and make them learn how to swim!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe have a few things we look for in moderators:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1) Minimum age 18 years old, for legal reasons (tropical years, not siderial).\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2) Have a good understanding of the English language. A second language is valuable but not required, a number of our mods are unilingual.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n3) The person is expected to have been contributing for a long time in a positive way to the community and shown a willingness to adapt to and abide by the rules. Post count and rep points don\u0027t count, but a hard-earned good reputation and the respect of others is vital.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n4) The prospective moderator must be friendly and have a desire to help others.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n5) Must definitely not have any craving for position or power.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n6) Must be willing to do thankless tasks in their free time that very few people, if any, will ever notice, and to occasionally be on the receiving end of unkind, abusive messages whilst being able to keep objectivity and without responding in the same manner.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:8px;\u0022\u003E\u003Csup\u003E[1]\u003C/sup\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/103121-how-does-one-become-a-moderator/\u0026amp;do=findComment\u0026amp;comment=1799822\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EAdapted from the original by Red Iron Crown\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-06-16T05:29:05Z\u0022 title=\u002206/16/2021 05:29  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EJune 16, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by Dman979\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EFormatting.\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Souptime","CreatedById":204451,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-16T05:32:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223989859\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221623821308\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022123837\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Dman979\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, Dman979 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn my case, I was approached by \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/149302-darth-badie/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022149302\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/149302-darth-badie/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Darth Badie\u003C/a\u003E, who asked me if I was interested in being part of the moderator team. I said yes (after asking a bunch of questions), signed an \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Non-Disclosure Agreement\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Non-Disclosure Agreement\u0022\u003ENDA\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E, and was given a whole bunch of moderator permissions and access. We very much throw new moderators in the deep end and make them learn how to swim!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe have a few things we look for in moderators:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1) Minimum age 18 years old, for legal reasons (tropical years, not siderial).\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2) Have a good understanding of the English language. A second language is valuable but not required, a number of our mods are unilingual.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n3) The person is expected to have been contributing for a long time in a positive way to the community and shown a willingness to adapt to and abide by the rules. Post count and rep points don\u0027t count, but a hard-earned good reputation and the respect of others is vital.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n4) The prospective moderator must be friendly and have a desire to help others.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n5) Must definitely not have any craving for position or power.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n6) Must be willing to do thankless tasks in their free time that very few people, if any, will ever notice, and to occasionally be on the receiving end of unkind, abusive messages whilst being able to keep objectivity and without responding in the same manner.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni qualify for all those, except for number 1 \u003Cspan\u003E:[\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EGuess that cuts me outta the running\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-16T05:34:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe also don\u0027t have a particular need to bring on any new moderators for the moment. But maybe when you\u0027re old enough we will. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Starhelperdude","CreatedById":204462,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-16T12:03:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223989862\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221623821551\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022204451\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Souptime\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, Souptime said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni qualify for all those, except for number 1 \u003Cspan\u003E:[\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EGuess that cuts me outta the running\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nsame \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spaceman.Spiff","CreatedById":209133,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-16T15:38:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/27914-vanamonde/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002227914\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/27914-vanamonde/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Vanamonde\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0is no longer a Banana Ninja????\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat has happened?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"FleshJeb","CreatedById":111640,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-16T17:49:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223989859\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221623821308\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022123837\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Dman979\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 hours ago, Dman979 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1000-word essay\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow did you hold Snark down to 1000 words? \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"adsii1970","CreatedById":89014,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-16T21:08:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223990098\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221623865798\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022111640\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022FleshJeb\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, FleshJeb said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow did you hold Snark down to 1000 words? \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou don\u0027t. It is one of those impossible tasks in life. Similar to the one given to Sisyphus.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223990043\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221623857938\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022209133\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Spaceman.Spiff\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, Spaceman.Spiff said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/27914-vanamonde/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002227914\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/27914-vanamonde/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Vanamonde\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0is no longer a Banana Ninja????\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat has happened?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNothing. Every once in a while, we all go through a time when we simply want to change up our profile and avatar. You should know. How many avatars have you rotated through over the last six months?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Admiral Fluffy","CreatedById":210816,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-16T21:19:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223989859\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221623821308\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022123837\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Dman979\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n15 hours ago, Dman979 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe process of becoming a mod is actually quite grueling (I can say this as I did it just a few years ago). First, you must prepare your body by shaving everywhere and covering yourself in peanut butter. Then there\u0027s the physical, where you are tested for endurance and agility by running a 10km obstacle course in subzero temperatures while carrying a backpack full of wet sand. After that, you must write a 1000-word essay about the spirit of the KSP community and how you will preserve and protect it. That done, you move on to the Reverse Captcha, where you must read 1000 posts and determine which ones are spambots, miss more than one and you\u0027re out. Finally, after you have completed those tasks, you must submit your moderator registration fee of $1000 in cash to UomoCapra and he\u0027ll make you a moderator.\u003Csup\u003E[1]\u003C/sup\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022#\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/a\u003E \u003Cspan\u003EHide contents\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn my case, I was approached by \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/149302-darth-badie/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022149302\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/149302-darth-badie/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Darth Badie\u003C/a\u003E, who asked me if I was interested in being part of the moderator team. I said yes (after asking a bunch of questions), signed an \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Non-Disclosure Agreement\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Non-Disclosure Agreement\u0022\u003ENDA\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E, and was given a whole bunch of moderator permissions and access. We very much throw new moderators in the deep end and make them learn how to swim!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe have a few things we look for in moderators:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1) Minimum age 18 years old, for legal reasons (tropical years, not siderial).\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2) Have a good understanding of the English language. A second language is valuable but not required, a number of our mods are unilingual.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n3) The person is expected to have been contributing for a long time in a positive way to the community and shown a willingness to adapt to and abide by the rules. Post count and rep points don\u0027t count, but a hard-earned good reputation and the respect of others is vital.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n4) The prospective moderator must be friendly and have a desire to help others.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n5) Must definitely not have any craving for position or power.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n6) Must be willing to do thankless tasks in their free time that very few people, if any, will ever notice, and to occasionally be on the receiving end of unkind, abusive messages whilst being able to keep objectivity and without responding in the same manner.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:8px;\u0022\u003E\u003Csup\u003E[1]\u003C/sup\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/103121-how-does-one-become-a-moderator/\u0026amp;do=findComment\u0026amp;comment=1799822\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EAdapted from the original by Red Iron Crown\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI qualify for some of those, definitely not 1 and 5.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-17T01:40:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI rotate my avatar now and then between images nice people have made for me.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dr. Kerbal","CreatedById":207217,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-17T05:12:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo moderators have a different UI and additional features? Like in the three dots there is like delete post option?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-17T05:19:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/v0xtql6.png\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022v0xtql6.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002284.00\u0022 height=\u0022942\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/v0xtql6.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deddly","CreatedById":62955,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-17T06:08:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223990450\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221623906757\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022207217\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Dr. Kerbal\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n54 minutes ago, Dr. Kerbal said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo moderators have a different UI and additional features? Like in the three dots there is like delete post option?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022iBvsYj3.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002248.64\u0022 height=\u0022394\u0022 width=\u0022810\u00